(secondQuint)Capsule Endoscopy in Obscure GI Bleeding.

 The purpose of this study is to conduct a cost-effectiveness analysis of wireless capsule endoscopy in the investigation of patients with overt obscure gastrointestinal bleeding.

 To inform this analysis, a randomized controlled trial of capsule endoscopy compared with standard care will be conducted.

 Patients randomized 1:1.

